---
import Layout from './layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  title="Why Health Testing Matters in Dog Breeding"
  description="Learn about the importance of health testing in responsible dog breeding practices."
>
  <!-- Blog Post Content -->
  <section class="text-bg-dark py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2">
          <!-- Blog Heading, Category, and Date -->
          <div class="mb-4">
            <span class="badge bg-gray-800 fs-6 mb-2">Health</span>
            <h1 class="fw-semibold mb-2">Why Health Testing Matters in Dog Breeding</h1>
            <p><i class="ri-calendar-line me-1"></i>12 Jan 2025</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Cover Image -->
          <div class="mb-4">
            <img
              src="/dist/assets/img/breederspot-images/german-shepherd-1.jpg"
              alt="Blog Cover"
              class="img-fluid rounded"
              style="max-height: 400px; object-fit: cover; width: 100%;"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Blog Content -->
          <div class="mb-4">
            <p>
              Breeding dogs responsibly requires more than just a passion for the breed — it demands
              a commitment to health and genetic screening. Health testing plays a pivotal role in
              reducing inherited diseases and ensuring the well-being of future litters.
            </p>
            <p>
              Through responsible breeding practices, including thorough health evaluations,
              breeders contribute to the long-term health of dog populations. Tests such as hip
              evaluations, genetic screenings, and cardiac exams help breeders make informed pairing
              decisions.
            </p>
            <p>
              Investing in health testing also builds trust with prospective puppy buyers,
              reinforces ethical breeding standards, and ultimately leads to healthier, happier
              pets.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Share Button -->
          <div class="mb-4">
            <button class="btn btn-lg btn-outline-light">
              <i class="ri-share-line me-1"></i> Share this post
            </button>
          </div>

          <!-- Author Section -->
          <div class="d-flex align-items-center border-top pt-4 mb-5">
            <img
              src="/dist/assets/img/avatars/avatar1.jpg"
              alt="Author Image"
              class="rounded-circle me-3"
              width="64"
              height="64"
            />
            <div>
              <h6 class="mb-1">
                <a href="#" class="text-light text-decoration-none">Jane Smith</a>
              </h6>

              <p class="mb-0">Certified canine health advocate with 10+ years of experience.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Similar Posts -->
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h4 class="mb-4">Similar Posts</h4>
            <div class="row g-4">
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card text-bg-gray-800 h-100 p-0">
                  <img
                    src="/dist/assets/img/breederspot-images/german-shepherd-1.jpg"
                    class="card-img-top"
                    alt="Similar Post 1"
                  />
                  <div class="card-body p-3">
                    <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none link-light"
                      ><h5 class="card-title">
                        Puppy Mills vs. Ethical Breeders: The Difference
                      </h5></a
                    >
                    <p class="card-text mb-2">
                      Comparing unethical breeding operations to responsible ones, with clear
                      distinctions.
                    </p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-link link-light p-0">Read more</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card text-bg-gray-800 h-100 p-0">
                  <img
                    src="/dist/assets/img/breederspot-images/german-shepherd-1.jpg"
                    class="card-img-top"
                    alt="Similar Post 2"
                  />
                  <div class="card-body p-3">
                    <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none link-light"
                      ><h5 class="card-title">The True Cost of a Well-Bred Puppy</h5></a
                    >
                    <p class="card-text mb-2">
                      Why puppies from ethical breeders cost more and what goes into responsible
                      pricing.
                    </p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-link link-light p-0">Read more</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section
    class="position-relative text-light text-center"
    style="background-image: url('/dist/assets/img/breederspot-images/german-shepherd-1.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center; height: 500px;"
  >
    <!-- Overlay -->
    <div class="position-absolute top-0 start-0 w-100 h-100 bg-dark opacity-75"></div>
    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="position-relative d-flex flex-column justify-content-center h-100 px-3">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-6 offset-lg-3">
          <h5 class="display-6 fw-semibold mb-2">Stay connected with the pack</h5>
          <p class="fs-5 mb-4">
            Subscribe to our newsletter for updates on upcoming litters, training tips, and stories
            from our shepherd family — straight to your inbox.
          </p>
          <!-- Email Form -->
          <form class="row g-2 justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-sm-9">
              <input
                type="email"
                class="form-control form-control-lg"
                placeholder="Enter your email"
                required=""
              />
              <div
                data-lastpass-icon-root=""
                style="position: relative !important; height: 0px !important; width: 0px !important; float: left !important;"
              >
              </div><div
                data-lastpass-icon-root=""
                style="position: relative !important; height: 0px !important; width: 0px !important; float: left !important;"
              >
              </div><div
                data-lastpass-icon-root=""
                style="position: relative !important; height: 0px !important; width: 0px !important; float: left !important;"
              >
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-3">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg w-100">Notify Me</button>
            </div>
          </form>
          <!-- Small note -->
          <p class="mt-3 mb-0">We send only what matters. No spam, ever.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
